graph LR
    KVCD[llm-d-kv-cache<br/>KV-Cache Indexing<br/>& Scoring Library]

    %% Primary Consumer (Internal Platform)
    InfSched[llm-d-inference-scheduler] -->|Go library import<br/>pkg/kvcache| KVCD

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    KVCD -->|ZMQ PUB/SUB<br/>KVEvent transport| ZeroMQ[ZeroMQ / libzmq<br/>System package]
    KVCD -->|CGo interop<br/>Embedded tokenization| Python312[Python 3.12<br/>3.12.x]
    KVCD -->|Tokenization runtime<br/>Chat template rendering| vLLM[vLLM<br/>0.18.0+rhaiv.4]
    KVCD -->|Model/tokenizer downloads<br/>HTTPS/443| HFHub[Hugging Face Hub<br/>>= 0.36.0]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    KVCD -.->|Distributed index backend<br/>6379/TCP, Optional TLS| Redis[Redis/Valkey<br/>Any version]
    KVCD -.->|OTLP trace export<br/>gRPC/4317| OTELCollector[OpenTelemetry Collector<br/>Any OTLP-compatible]
    KVCD -.->|Metrics scrape<br/>HTTP| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Any version]

    %% Internal Platform Dependencies
    vLLMPods[vLLM Pods] -->|ZMQ PUB/SUB<br/>KVEvents| KVCD
    SGLangPods[SGLang Pods] -.->|ZMQ PUB/SUB<br/>KVEvents (alt engine)| KVCD

    %% Platform Infrastructure
    KVCD -->|Pod discovery<br/>HTTPS/443, mTLS| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP]

    %% Storage
    LlmdFS[llmd_fs_backend<br/>vLLM Plugin] -->|Shared storage<br/>File I/O| SharedPVC[NFS/PVC<br/>Shared Storage]
    PVCEvictor[PVC Evictor<br/>Python Utility] -->|Evict stale files<br/>File I/O| SharedPVC

